{"tid":1933272,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"［文宣］外國傳媒詳細測試 微信、YY早在12月審查武漢肺炎内容 / 抖音內部文件 揭會審查樣衰、政治不正確內容","createTime":"2020-03-19T07:51:24.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-23T01:07:41.000Z","uid":48083,"like":99,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":85,"replies":[{"pid":"d1696dfaf6b91cdf3d0ed9d52fef983cb513c74d","tid":1933272,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-19T07:51:24.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://citizenlab.ca/2020/03/censored-contagion-how-information-on-the-coronavirus-is-managed-on-chinese-social-media/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcitizenlab.ca%2F2020%2F03%2Fcensored-contagion-how-information-on-the-coronavirus-is-managed-on-chinese-social-media%2F&d=vBgtTLCpkGvyAljQauEZFS3KoYHjImyLH66vjnFGY4M%3D&h=1d7dd110\" target=\"_blank\">https://citizenlab.ca/2020/03/censored-contagion-how-information-on-the-coronavirus-is-managed-on-chinese-social-media/</a><br />\n<br />\n兩個apps唔同審查既方法<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1O9hCJ2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1O9hCJ2.png&h=1e494748&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n有用一個美國一個中國account 測試<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pABWThr.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpABWThr.png&h=96bb3506&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n發現審查既字眼<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/iRBvXKa.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FiRBvXKa.png&h=43f40409&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4URf8QT.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4URf8QT.png&h=29bc0126&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4V8qMCD.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4V8qMCD.png&h=3f332dc9&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aVoY6CJ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaVoY6CJ.png&h=f3043975&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/P0PhCKq.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FP0PhCKq.png&h=978d0772&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aMUJyhM.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaMUJyhM.png&h=0c1015e9&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZsaMv4s.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZsaMv4s.png&h=de5f3b77&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/K3m4hKu.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FK3m4hKu.png&h=c818e2e9&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ef162f004f41aebd4dcc71c08ddd459881aacdcc","tid":1933272,"uid":48083,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-19T07:51:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rZ9Nfyy.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrZ9Nfyy.png&h=2eaf2f07&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7cca0a32cbb181ff8f6cd3c2a46254c4da340909","tid":1933272,"uid":48083,"like":21,"dislike":0,"score":21,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-19T07:55:34.000Z","msg":"TikTok Told Moderators to Suppress Posts by &ldquo;Ugly&rdquo; People and the Poor to Attract New Users<br />\n<br />\nThe makers of TikTok⋯⋯⋯nstructed moderators to suppress posts created by users deemed too ugly, poor, or disabled for the platform,<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"> according to internal documents obtained by The Intercept</span></strong>. <br />\n<br />\nThese same documents show moderators were also told to censor political speech in TikTok livestreams, punishing those who harmed &ldquo;national honor&rdquo; or broadcast streams about &ldquo;state organs such as police&rdquo; with bans from the platform.<br />\n<br />\n⋯⋯Any number of the document&rsquo;s rules could be invoked to block discussion of a wide range of topics embarrassing to government authorities: &ldquo;Defamation &hellip; towards civil servants, political or religious leaders&rdquo; as well as towards &ldquo;the families of related leaders&rdquo; has been, under the policy, punishable with a terminated stream and a daylong suspension. <br />\n<br />\nAny broadcasts deemed by ByteDance&rsquo;s moderators to be &ldquo;endangering national security&rdquo; or even &ldquo;national honor and interests&rdquo; were punished with a permanent ban, as were &ldquo;uglification or distortion of local or other countries&rsquo; history,&rdquo; with the &ldquo;Tiananmen Square incidents&rdquo; cited as only one of three real world examples. <br />\n<br />\nA &ldquo;Personal live broadcast about state organs such as police office, military etc,&rdquo; would knock your stream offline for three days, while documenting military or police activity would get you kicked off for that day (would-be protestors, take note).<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://theintercept.com/2020/03/16/tiktok-app-moderators-users-discrimination/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftheintercept.com%2F2020%2F03%2F16%2Ftiktok-app-moderators-users-discrimination%2F&d=vBgtTLCpkGvyAljQauEZFS3KoYHjImyLH66vjnFGY4M%3D&h=838fd12f\" target=\"_blank\">https://theintercept.com/2020/03/16/tiktok-app-moderators-users-discrimination/</a>"},{"pid":"0b42e840ce8241273bffd9431d23419eb74dec1c","tid":1933272,"uid":264887,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-19T07:58:35.000Z","msg":"Up"},{"pid":"b05d10166cfbda987a9fe906d3d641739728b95d","tid":1933272,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-19T08:01:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e3b1189d28f747588e799a0054573c6775f79f96","tid":1933272,"uid":122275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-19T08:03:09.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"3286d8b258272fd4f3903d2de5969abcee97fb4f","tid":1933272,"uid":150930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-19T08:05:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"54de32d